source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_ERROR_DISABLE<tab>My apologies, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>, but we're not able to accept new clientele at present.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_ERROR_DISABLE<tab>Pardonnez-moi, notre comptoir n'est pas encore opérationnel. Je vous prie de bien vouloir revenir plus tard, lorsque nous serons ouverts.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_ERROR_RETAINER_COUNT<tab>It does not appear you have any retainers in your employ at this time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_ERROR_RETAINER_COUNT<tab>Je regrette, mais vous n'avez ac<var 16 /var>tu<var 16 /var>el<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment aucun servant à votre service...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_ERROR_RETAINER_CHARGE<tab>You cannot perform this action until you have purchased the services of an additional retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_ERROR_RETAINER_CHARGE<tab>Impossible d'effectuer cette action. Vous devez d'abord vous réabonner au service de servants.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_DEFAULT_TALK_01<tab>Ah, <var 29 EB02 /var>. Welcome to Musica Universalis. How may I help you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_DEFAULT_TALK_01<tab>Bonjour, <var 08 E905 ((Madame)) ((Monsieur)) /var>. Bienvenue à Musica Universalis, le quartier marchand de Cristarium. Que puis-je faire pour vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_TALK_01<tab>May I have the name of a retainer you wish to dispatch? The Crystal Exarch has asked that Feo Ul serve as their intermediary. How they would accomplish this, well... I thought it better not to ask.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_TALK_01<tab>Choisissez le servant que vous désirez assigner au marché de Cristarium.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_ASK<tab>Send <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> to the Crystarium?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_ASK<tab>Assigner <var 29 EA02 /var> à Cristarium<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_SUCCESS<tab>Very good. I will see to it Feo Ul contact them right away.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_SUCCESS<tab>Le servant “<var 29 EA02 /var>” est désormais inscrit au marché de Cristarium.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_ALREADY<tab>I do believe that retainer has already been dispatched to the Crystarium.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_ALREADY<tab>Ce servant est déjà inscrit au marché de Cristarium.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_FAILED<tab>The retainer was unable to meet with Feo Ul.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_REGISTER_FAILED<tab>Impossible d'inscrire le servant au marché.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_TITLE<tab>What would you like to do?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_TITLE<tab>Que voulez-vous faire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER<tab>Dispatch a retainer to the Crystarium.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_REGISTER<tab>Inscrire un servant à Cristarium

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_ABOUT<tab>Ask about the Crystarium market.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_ABOUT<tab>En savoir plus sur le marché de Cristarium

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_CASHBACK<tab>View market tax rates.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_CASHBACK<tab>S'enquérir des taxes aux marchés

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Nothing.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Annuler

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_ABOUT_01<tab>The Crystarium's market is by no means large, but you're more than welcome to sell your wares here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_ABOUT_01<tab>Le marché de Cristarium, ou Musica Universalis comme nous l'appelons, est le principal lieu d'échange de la cité. Si vous avez des servants, c'est ici qu'ils officieront.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_ABOUT_02<tab>The Crystal Exarch tells me Feo Ul has been charged with retrieving your things, from...where are you from again, exactly?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_MAIN_MENU_ABOUT_02<tab>J'ai ouï dire que dans votre cas, une Pixie vous servirait d'intermédiaire<var 1D /var>? Ne vous en faites pas, ça ne pose aucun problème.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_TITLE<tab>Current Market Tax Rates:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_TITLE<tab>Taxes des marchés

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK<tab><var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var>: Reduced
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK<tab><var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var><var 1D /var>: taxe réduite

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_NONE<tab><var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var>: Normal
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_NONE<tab><var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var><var 1D /var>: taxe normale

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_ABOUT<tab>Learn about Market Tax
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_ABOUT<tab>Savoir à quoi servent les réductions de taxe

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_CANCEL<tab>Return
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ASK_CANCEL<tab>Retour

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_NO_CASHBACK<tab>Tax on items sold in the <var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var> markets is the normal rate of <var 20 E803 /var>%.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_NO_CASHBACK<tab>La taxe sur les objets vendus à <var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var> est au taux normal de <var 20 E803 /var>% du prix de vente.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK<tab>Tax on items sold in the <var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var> markets is reduced to <var 20 E805 /var>% until <var 07 E803 /var><var 08 E4E94E04 (( <var 20 DC /var>/<var 20 DE /var>/<var 20 DF /var>)) ((<var 20 DE /var>/<var 20 DC /var>/<var 20 DF /var>)) /var> (Earth date).
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK<tab>La taxe sur les objets vendus à <var 28 ((Town)) E80201 /var> est réduite de <var 20 E804 /var>% jusqu'au <var 07 E803 /var><var 20 DC /var>.<var 20 DE /var>.<var 20 DF /var> (temps réel)<var 1D /var>! Le prélèvement est donc de <var 20 E805 /var>% du prix de vente.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ABOUT_01<tab>To make their markets more attractive to prospective sellers, cities will often lower the percentage of tax that is collected from each sale.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ABOUT_01<tab>Il arrive souvent que les cités réduisent la taxe qu'elles prélèvent sur les ventes afin de favoriser l'activité de leur marché.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ABOUT_02<tab>Reduced tax rate periods can end earlier than indicated if areas require maintenance.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERMARKETREGISTER_00581_CASHBACK_ABOUT_02<tab>Les périodes de réduction peuvent être plus courtes qu'annoncées si une maintenance est nécessaire dans la zone concernée.
